Fax Wizard - Items to include

Specifies the fax elements to be printed.

To access this command...

Choose File - Wizards - Fax - Items to include


Logo

Includes a company logo.

Date

Includes a date field.

Type of message

Includes a communication type line. Select the line from the list box.

Subject line

Includes a subject line.

Salutation

Includes a salutation. Select the salutation from the list box.

Complimentary close

Includes a greeting. Select the greeting from the list box.

Footer

Includes a footer.

Go to Fax Wizard - Sender and Recipient
